    <h2>7. Coffee Grinders: The Equipment Most Buyers Forget</h2>
    <p>A commercial espresso machine without a matching commercial grinder is like buying a sports car and fitting it with budget tyres. The grinder is as important as the espresso machine — arguably more so. Fresh grinding immediately before extraction is what separates excellent espresso from mediocre espresso.</p>
    <p>Never buy pre-ground coffee for commercial espresso service. And never use a domestic or cheap grinder with a commercial espresso machine — the grind consistency will be poor and your extraction will suffer regardless of how good the machine is.</p>

